    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up in the dark and see Stella in front of you, revealing a cruel truth: Earth has been destroyed by alien invaders, humanity has fallen, and you are the last person in the Universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stella is an AI that offers you the only remaining option: revenge against the invaders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must face the entire Galaxy, and along with Stella and her shards, embark on an exciting journey to the very center of the Galaxy, battling various enemies and anomalies along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Stella and help her cleanse the Galaxy. The closer you get to the center of the Galaxy, the more dangerous enemies await you, and the darker secrets of the catastrophe you will uncover.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Control a variety of different characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044780/extras/2d9e2a2c8843bababbbf76b9b8d8306a.poster.avif?t=1771864394\" width=700 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044780/extras/2d9e2a2c8843bababbbf76b9b8d8306a.webm?t=1771864394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044780/extras/2d9e2a2c8843bababbbf76b9b8d8306a.mp4?t=1771864394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Apply and combine their abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044780/extras/c1e4cf8d2cb9b11a44baa780049d820e.poster.avif?t=1771864394\" width=700 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044780/extras/c1e4cf8d2cb9b11a44baa780049d820e.webm?t=1771864394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044780/extras/c1e4cf8d2cb9b11a44baa780049d820e.mp4?t=1771864394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect strong characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044780/extras/3ea41152a12eb6cc108bbfb7ddb9d270.poster.avif?t=1771864394\" width=700 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044780/extras/3ea41152a12eb6cc108bbfb7ddb9d270.webm?t=1771864394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044780/extras/3ea41152a12eb6cc108bbfb7ddb9d270.mp4?t=1771864394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 regions with their own conditions, enemies, and bosses</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Characters with a variety of weapons and abilities.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dynamic cosmos where various events are constantly happening.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete missions for each region to advance to the next level.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase character ranks by enhancing them.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
